summary: Need a nice Crossbow to fit with your falmer armor set? so here is a wonderful new crossbow maid out of charus chitin.
descriptionHtml:
Need a nice Crossbow to fit with your falmer armor set? so here is a wonderful new crossbow maid out of charus chitin. 
one model of the crossbow and 100 arrows can be found in Nchuand-zel (control room), Mzinchaleft (with the falmer armor set), and in black reach (by the throne in the middle).
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Also check out my new Blessings of the Madgod Mod: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/38348/?
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
this mod requires dawnguard
